&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mandarinoriental.com/miami/fine-dining/azul/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Azul website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact Azul by phone at +1-305-913-8358 or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:momia-restaurants@mohg.com&quot;&gt;momia-restaurants@mohg.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
